Whenever crystalline decays are spawned, a title
will be shown in the middle of the screen.

Whenever a light orb is forming, a title
will be shown in the middle of the screen.

Whenever a shadowling is killed, a title
will be shown in the middle of the screen.

Automatic: Always send a request to Wynn API for
raid stats upon joining a party.

Manual: Append a message in the player's chat
that, when clicked, will query and display
the raid stats for party members.

Reminds you to not pick additional buffs
to avoid a pull reward penalty.

Keeps track of what your party members have chosen
for their raid buffs. As of now, it is not
used for anything.
text.config.sequoia.option.territoryFeat:
Shows extra information about the captured territory
such as: produced resources, treasury and defences.
By default, the hotkey is set to 'N'.
text.config.sequoia.option.verboseLoggin:
Useful for debugging purposes, you should only
enable this if asked by the developer.
